'''全球500佳环境奖'''（Global 500 Roll of Honour for Environmental Achievement），又称'''世界环保500佳'''或'''联合国环境保护奖'''，是由[[联合国环境规划署|联合国环境规划署]]于1987年设立的<ref name="xinhua2002">{{cite web  | language =zh-hans  | publisher =  | title =深圳和内蒙古敖汉旗获全球环境“500佳”称号  | url =http://news.xinhuanet.com/zhengfu/2002-06/05/content_424899.htm  | author =  | date =2002-06-05  | accessdate =2009-04-12  | archive-date =2004-11-30  | archive-url =https://web.archive.org/web/20041130112331/http://news.xinhuanet.com/zhengfu/2002-06/05/content_424899.htm  | dead-url =no  }}</ref>，旨在表彰对[[环境保护|环境保护]]做出杰出贡献的组织和个人的奖项。该奖在每年[[世界环境日|世界环境日]]颁发。截止2003年，共有683个组织和个人获奖<ref name="global500">{{cite web  | language =en  | publisher =[[UNEP|UNEP]]  | title =About the Global 500  | url =http://www.global500.org/about.html  | author =  | date =  | accessdate =2009-04-12  | deadurl =yes  | archiveurl =https://web.archive.org/web/20090217230113/http://global500.org/about.html  | archivedate =2009-02-17  }}</ref>。从2004年起，联合国环境规划署设立新奖项——“[[地球卫士奖|地球卫士奖]]”代替该奖项<ref name="cepf2006">{{cite web  | language =zh-hans  | publisher =[[中华环境保护基金会|中华环境保护基金会]]  | title =地球卫士奖  | url =http://www.cepf.org.cn/xmjs/qtxm/dqws/200612/t20061228_98969.htm  | author =  | date =2006-12-28  | accessdate =2009-04-12  | archive-date =2009-03-25  | archive-url =https://web.archive.org/web/20090325101012/http://www.cepf.org.cn/xmjs/qtxm/dqws/200612/t20061228_98969.htm  | dead-url =no  }}</ref>。

